OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778073066
OL,3,CAdam Peaty praises teen swimming
OL,4,Ccompetitor's "impressive" talent
OL,6,FOlympic gold medallist Adam Peaty
OL,7,Fspoke to ITV Channel about Jersey
OL,8,Fswimmer Filip Nowacki's "impressive"
OL,9,Ftalent.
OL,11,FIn April, 18-year-old Nowacki won his
OL,12,Ffirst British senior title after
OL,13,Fclaiming gold in the 200m breaststroke
OL,14,Fat the Aquatics GB Swimming
OL,15,FChampionships.
OL,17,FPeaty, who is widely regarded as the
OL,18,Fbest breaststroker of all time,
OL,19,Fdescribed his teen competitor as an
OL,20,F"impressive young man coming through
OL,21,Fthe ranks very fast".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
