FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778073066
OL,3,CAdam Peaty praises teen swimming
OL,4,Ccompetitor's "impressive" talent
OL,6,FNowacki has also qualified for the
OL,7,FEuropean Championships in Paris in
OL,8,FAugust, recording the third-fastest
OL,9,F100m breaststroke time in the world
OL,10,Fthis year as he finished just behind
OL,11,Ftriple Olympic champion Peaty.
OL,13,FThe Jersey teen will also represent
OL,14,Fthe island at the Commonwealth Games
OL,15,Fin Glasgow in July.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
