FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778073066
OL,3,CAdam Peaty praises teen swimming
OL,4,Ccompetitor's "impressive" talent
OL,6,FPeaty, 31, told ITV Channel: "He's
OL,7,Falready so fast - especially in the
OL,8,F200m, and now he's getting down a
OL,9,F100m, so it's going to be an
OL,10,Finteresting Commonwealth Games for
OL,11,Fhim, and I'll enjoy racing him."
OL,13,FThe Staffordshire-born athlete
OL,14,Fbelieves Nowacki also stands a strong
OL,15,Fchance at winning medals at the 2028
OL,16,FOlympics in Los Angeles.
OL,18,F"It's your first Olympic game - you
OL,19,Fdon't want to go there and just be a
OL,20,Ftourist, you want to be there to win a
OL,21,Fmedal.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778073066
OL,3,CAdam Peaty praises teen swimming
OL,4,Ccompetitor's "impressive" talent
OL,6,F"He will naturally progress into that
OL,7,Fthinking of bringing back gold medals,
OL,8,Fand also potentially world records,
OL,9,Fespecially in that 200 (metre)".
OL,11,FThe athlete explained that it will be
OL,12,Fthe Commonwealth Games where the
OL,13,FJersey native has the potential to
OL,14,F"step it up a level".
OL,16,FHe added that the 18-year-old has the
OL,17,Fspeed to compete at an elite 100m
OL,18,Flevel and the stamina to become world-
OL,19,Fclass in the 200m.
OL,26,@qD@XpmqD@^pn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
