PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778073066
OL,3,CAdam Peaty praises teen swimming
OL,4,Ccompetitor's "impressive" talent
OL,6,FPeaty also spoke about how impressive
OL,7,FNowacki is, given his smaller stature
OL,8,Fand tender age.
OL,10,F"I'm a power athlete, whereas
OL,11,F(Nowacki) can rely on that endurance
OL,12,Faspect quite a bit - both have proven
OL,13,Fto be very fast", although he noted
OL,14,Fthat the young swimmer will need to
OL,15,Fgain more body muscle in the future if
OL,16,Fhe wants to advance in the sport.
OL,26,@sD@ApmsD@Ipn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
