PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778073066
OL,3,CAdam Peaty praises teen swimming
OL,4,Ccompetitor's "impressive" talent
OL,6,FPeaty himself was just 19 when he
OL,7,Fattended his first Commonwealth Games
OL,8,Fin 2014 and won his first world record
OL,9,Fin the 50-metre breaststroke at the
OL,10,FEuropean Championships in Berlin at
OL,11,Fthe same age.
OL,13,FJust two years later, the Uttoxeter
OL,14,Fnative won his first Olympic gold
OL,15,Fmedal at the 2016 Rio Summer Olympics.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
