FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778073066
OL,3,CAdam Peaty praises teen swimming
OL,4,Ccompetitor's "impressive" talent
OL,6,FThe 31-year-old runs AP Race alongside
OL,7,Fhis training partner, Ed Baxter, which
OL,8,Fsupports the next generation of
OL,9,Fswimming talent through clinics,
OL,10,Fcompetitions, and coaching - something
OL,11,FNowacki is also involved with.
OL,13,F"Being able to be on poolside and
OL,14,Ftelling these swimmers exactly what it
OL,15,Ftakes, and if you don't make it,
OL,16,Fthinking about what skills you're
OL,17,Fgoing to bring through sport."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
