PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778073066
OL,3,CAdam Peaty praises teen swimming
OL,4,Ccompetitor's "impressive" talent
OL,6,FPeaty, who is married to Gordon
OL,7,FRamsay's daughter, Holly Ramsay, also
OL,8,Fexplained how sport has helped his
OL,9,Frelationship with his celebrity chef
OL,10,Ffather-in-law.
OL,12,F"I have a few values that align with
OL,13,FHolly (Ramsay) and her family, which
OL,14,Fare respect, work as hard as you can,
OL,15,Fand love what you do - anything else
OL,16,Fis a bonus".
OL,26,@uD@GpmuD@NpnxD@KO]
